'''Lucky Lower 13''' was an unconverted ballroom on the [[Mon Calamari Star Cruiser/Legends|Mon Calamari Star Cruiser]] [[Independence/Legends|''Independence'']], dating back to the ship's time as a pleasure cruiser and located in the aft quadrant of the ship. During the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], it served as a bar and its proximity to the pilot's lounge made it a popular location for off-duty pilots, as well and many of the engineering and administrative crew who worked in that quadrant. The room was darkened to accommodate the [[Quarren/Legends|Quarren]] crew members and tables and chairs were made to glow pink in the dark.

